data.description: Welcome to your new dream home nestled in the quiet community of Cherry Lake Oaks in Groveland, FL. From the moment you arrive, you'll notice its undeniable curb appeal, accentuated by a brick paver driveway and elegant palm trees. Stepping inside, the expansive open floor plan greets you, adorned with high ceilings, lots of natural sunlight and sleek, easy-to-maintain tile flooring. At the heart of the home lies the stunning kitchen, boasting a magnificent center island, gleaming granite countertops, and a cozy breakfast nook. Functionality meets style with its 42" cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and an eye-catching glass tile backsplash. A few steps away, the spacious primary bedroom emerges as the perfect sanctuary complemented by a luxurious ensuite bath equipped with separate dual sinks, a large soaking tub for those relaxing evenings, a framed glass shower, and a private water closet. But the beauty of this home doesn't stop indoors. Venture outside to discover a private covered lanai, a perfect spot to enjoy morning coffees or evening wind-downs, all while overlooking a vast backyard that awaits your personal touch. Nestled in a prime location, this community is mere minutes away from shopping, schools, a variety of restaurants, and provides easy highway access for those daily commutes or weekend getaways. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule your private showing today.
